OL,5, A mental health unit criticised over   
OL,6, the deaths of three teenagers was      
OL,7, "chaotic and unsafe", a report found.  
OL,9,FAn independent inquiry found "excessive
OL,10,Fand inappropriate" restraint was used  
OL,11,Fat Middlesbrough's West Lane Hospital. 
OL,13,FThe environment "facilitated           
OL,14,Fself-harm", said patients, and staff   
OL,15,Fwere told not to intervene unless it   
OL,16,Fwas likely to be fatal.                
OL,18,FTees, Esk and Wear Valley NHS          
OL,19,FFoundation Trust (TEWV) apologised and 
OL,20,Fsaid significant changes had been made.
